fields.name: Brio
fields.description: Entry-level hatchback, currently only produced in Indonesia for several Southeast Asian markets.

fields.name: Toyota Avalon
fields.description: When thrilling design meets cutting edge technology, the new generation of premium is born. The all-new 2019 Avalon is as dynamic as it is luxurious.

fields.name: Accord
fields.description: Mid-size sedan. Also available as the Inspire in China. Hybrid available.

fields.name: Toyota Tundra
fields.description: Beautiful red chenille stripe cushion.Complimentary to other cushions or as a stand alone statement piece.Woven on a luxurious polyester quality base. Cushion pattern is repeated on both sides.

fields.name: Toyota 86
fields.description: Toyota 86 is the unique sports car you've been waiting for. A Flat 4 Boxer Engine, rear wheel drive, dual exhaust, and a 7'' touchscreen, make this the car to take a look at.

fields.name: Elysion
fields.description: Chinese regional product based on the Asian Odyssey. Exclusively manufactured by Dongfeng Honda.

fields.name: N-One
fields.description: Retro-styled low-roof hatchback kei car with hinged rear doors.

fields.name: Toyota Prius
fields.description: From the sporty exterior to the high-tech, soft-touch interior, Prius has never had such a powerful presence.

fields.name: NSX
fields.description: Flagship sports car, available in North America as the Acura NSX.

fields.name: Toyota Highlander
fields.description: You may never hear “Are we there yet?” again. The 2021 Highlander & Highlander Hybrid have the safety, performance, and fun factor to keep your entire family content through every adventure.

fields.name: Audi TT
fields.description: Two decades after its debut, the Audi TT Coupé still inspires with its design language and pure driving pleasure.

fields.name: Audi A1
fields.description: The new Audi A1 combines dynamic design with everyday practicality. It is the perfect urban companion that doesn’t compromise on style or detail. The new refined interior offers new levels of spaciousness and comfort, making it the perfect drive for longer adventures.

fields.name: Audi A4
fields.description: Thanks to a new language of design and an almost completely new body, the sporty character of the Audi A4 saloon comes into play more than ever: it appears dynamic and powerful while attractive and aesthetic at the same time. A high-quality and functionally designed interior, innovative technologies in the fields of digitisation, infotainment and driver assistance systems, and powerful engines round off the overall package.
